ng.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\"><strong>Gi&aacute; b&aacute;n</strong>: 270.000đ/ hộp 15 g&oacute;i.</span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.020.000đ/ hộp 60 g&oacute;i</span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\"><strong>Bảo quản</strong>: Nơi kh&ocirc; r&aacute;o, tho&aacute;ng m&aacute;t, tr&aacute;nh &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng mặt trời.</span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\"><strong>Số ĐK:</strong> 20291/2013/ATTP - XNCB.</span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">Sản phẩm kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; thuốc v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; t&aacute;c dụng thay thế thuốc chữa bệnh</span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\"><strong>Xuất xứ</strong>: Nhật Bản</span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\"><strong>Li&ecirc;n hệ</strong><strong> mua h&agrave;ng:</strong></span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">HT cửa h&agrave;ng EnMax &ndash; Số 5/189 Giảng V&otilde;, Đống Đa, HN.</span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">Hotline: 0932 292 136.</span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\"><strong>Giao h&agrave;ng tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quốc, nhận h&agrave;ng thanh to&aacute;n.</strong></span></span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&n